data.text:
The Brain Bowl Incubation

Sheldon goes to great lengths to convince Amy that they should have a baby together after they successfully complete a scientific experiment using DNA samples from both of them.

The Wood

Larry may be banned from his country club if he does not clean up his dirty locker, and he is forced to steal a golf club from a deceased person's casket.

The Weatherman

Larry suspects the weatherman is deliberately delivering inaccurate forecasts. Plus, he manages to scare everyone with images of his tooth plaque.

Where There's Smoke, There's Ire

Mandy's parents are not happy when they find she has taken up vaping, while it brings back nostalgic memories for Vanessa. Meanwhile, Ryan and Kristin find a safe hiding in the cellar.
